cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV 

This paper deals with unsupervised cross-lingual embeddings mapping and its application to product classification matching. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI), and computer vision (cs.CV).
